    <div class="spotlight-leadin promoBlurb selected">
      <h3><a href="http://www.portfolio.com/business-news/2011/03/17/importers-worried-about-sake-business-following-japan-earthquake">
A Sake Story</a></h3>
      <div class="promoText">
How badly has Japan’s massive earthquake affected its sake breweries? One U.S.-based sake entrepreneur weighs in. And a top business-continuity expert says you can’t be too careful about having multiple suppliers.
 <a href="http://www.portfolio.com/business-news/2011/03/17/importers-worried-about-sake-business-following-japan-earthquake">Read More</a></div>
    </div>
    <div class="spotlight-leadin promoBlurb" style="display: none;">
      <h3><a href="http://www.portfolio.com/companies-executives/2011/03/21/safetyweb-founders-launch-myid-to-monitor-online-identity">
On the Trail for "Digital Footprints"</a></h3>
      <div class="promoText">
Keeping tabs on your digital reputation can be a real challenge. But one company that's found success assisting parents keep track of their kids' activities online is now trying to help people control their own personal information.
 <a href="http://www.portfolio.com/companies-executives/2011/03/21/safetyweb-founders-launch-myid-to-monitor-online-identity">Read More</a></div>
